var book = {
	"name": "Hebrews",
	"numChapters": 13,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Long ago, at many times and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29948A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29948A\"></sup>in many ways, God spoke to our fathers by the prophets,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29949B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29949B\"></sup>in these last days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29949C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29949C\"></sup>he has spoken to us by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29949D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29949D\"></sup>his Son, whom he appointed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29949E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29949E\"></sup>the heir of all things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29949F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29949F\"></sup>through whom also he created <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29949G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29949G\"></sup>the world.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He is the radiance of the glory of God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29950H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29950H\"></sup>the exact imprint of his nature, and he upholds the universe by the word of his power. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29950I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29950I\"></sup>After making purification for sins, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29950J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29950J\"></sup>he sat down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29950K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29950K\"></sup>at the right hand of the Majesty on high,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>having become as much superior to angels as the name <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29951L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29951L\"></sup>he has inherited is more excellent than theirs.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For to which of the angels did God ever say,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29952M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29952M\"></sup>“You are my Son,today I have begotten you”?Or again,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29952N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29952N\"></sup>“I will be to him a father,and he shall be to me a son”?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And again, when he brings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29953O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29953O\"></sup>the firstborn into the world, he says,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29953P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29953P\"></sup>“Let all God's angels worship him.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Of the angels he says,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29954Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29954Q\"></sup>“He makes his angels winds,and his ministers a flame of fire.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But of the Son he says,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29955R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29955R\"></sup>“Your throne, O God, is forever and ever,the scepter of uprightness is the scepter of your kingdom.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You have loved righteousness and hated wickedness;therefore God, your God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29956S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29956S\"></sup>has anointed youwith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29956T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29956T\"></sup>the oil of gladness beyond your companions.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29957U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29957U\"></sup>“You, Lord, laid the foundation of the earth in the beginning,and the heavens are the work of your hands;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>they will perish, but you remain;they will all wear out like a garment,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>like a robe you will roll them up,like a garment they will be changed.But you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29959V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29959V\"></sup>the same,and your years will have no end.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And to which of the angels has he ever said,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29960W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29960W\"></sup>“Sit at my right hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29960X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29960X\"></sup>until I make your enemies a footstool for your feet”?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Are they not all ministering spirits <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29961Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29961Y\"></sup>sent out to serve for the sake of those who are to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29961Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29961Z\"></sup>inherit salvation?"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Therefore we must pay much closer attention to what we have heard, lest we drift away from it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For since <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29963A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29963A\"></sup>the message declared by angels proved to be reliable, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29963B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29963B\"></sup>every transgression or disobedience received a just <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29963C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29963C\"></sup>retribution,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29964D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29964D\"></sup>how shall we escape if we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29964E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29964E\"></sup>neglect such a great salvation? It was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29964F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29964F\"></sup>declared at first by the Lord, and it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29964G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29964G\"></sup>attested to us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29964H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29964H\"></sup>by those who heard,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29965I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29965I\"></sup>while God also bore witness <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29965J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29965J\"></sup>by signs and wonders and various miracles and by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29965K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29965K\"></sup>gifts of the Holy Spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29965L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29965L\"></sup>distributed according to his will.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For it was not to angels that God subjected the world <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29966M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29966M\"></sup>to come, of which we are speaking.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>It has been testified somewhere,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29967N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29967N\"></sup>“What is man, that you are mindful of him,or the son of man, that you care for him?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You made him for a little while lower than the angels;you have crowned him with glory and honor,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>putting everything in subjection under his feet.”Now in putting everything in subjection to him, he left nothing outside his control. At present, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29969O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29969O\"></sup>we do not yet see everything in subjection to him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But we see him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29970P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29970P\"></sup>who for a little while was made lower than the angels, namely Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29970Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29970Q\"></sup>crowned with glory and honor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29970R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29970R\"></sup>because of the suffering of death, so that by the grace of God he might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29970S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29970S\"></sup>taste death <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29970T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29970T\"></sup>for everyone.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29971U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29971U\"></sup>was fitting that he, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29971V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29971V\"></sup>for whom and by whom all things exist, in bringing many sons <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29971W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29971W\"></sup>to glory, should make the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29971X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29971X\"></sup>founder of their salvation <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29971Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29971Y\"></sup>perfect through suffering.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29972Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29972Z\"></sup>he who sanctifies and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29972AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29972AA\"></sup>those who are sanctified <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29972AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29972AB\"></sup>all have one source. That is why he is not ashamed to call them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29972AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29972AC\"></sup>brothers,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>saying,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29973AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29973AD\"></sup>“I will tell of your name to my brothers;in the midst of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29973AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29973AE\"></sup>congregation I will sing your praise.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And again,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29974AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29974AF\"></sup>“I will put my trust in him.”And again,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29974AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29974AG\"></sup>“Behold, I and the children <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29974AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29974AH\"></sup>God has given me.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Since therefore the children share in flesh and blood, he himself likewise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29975AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29975AI\"></sup>partook of the same things, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29975AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29975AJ\"></sup>through death he might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29975AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29975AK\"></sup>destroy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29975AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29975AL\"></sup>the one who has the power of death, that is, the devil,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and deliver all those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29976AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29976AM\"></sup>through fear of death were subject to lifelong slavery.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For surely it is not angels that he helps, but he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29977AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29977AN\"></sup>helps the offspring of Abraham.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29978AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29978AO\"></sup>to be made like his brothers in every respect, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29978AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29978AP\"></sup>so that he might become a merciful and faithful high priest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29978AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29978AQ\"></sup>in the service of God, to make propitiation for the sins of the people.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For because he himself has suffered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29979AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29979AR\"></sup>when tempted, he is able to help those who are being tempted."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Therefore, holy brothers, you who share in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29980A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29980A\"></sup>a heavenly calling, consider Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29980B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29980B\"></sup>the apostle and high priest of our confession,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>who was faithful to him who appointed him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29981C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29981C\"></sup>just as Moses also was faithful in all God's house.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For Jesus has been counted worthy of more glory than Moses—as much more glory as the builder of a house has more honor than the house itself.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>(For every house is built by someone, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29983D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29983D\"></sup>the builder of all things is God.)",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29984E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29984E\"></sup>Now Moses was faithful in all God's house <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29984F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29984F\"></sup>as a servant, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29984G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29984G\"></sup>to testify to the things that were to be spoken later,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>but Christ is faithful over God's house as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29985H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29985H\"></sup>a son. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29985I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29985I\"></sup>we are his house, if indeed we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29985J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29985J\"></sup>hold fast our confidence and our boasting in our hope.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore, as the Holy Spirit says,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29986K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29986K\"></sup>“Today, if you hear his voice,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>do not harden your hearts as in the rebellion,on the day of testing in the wilderness,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>where your fathers put me to the testand saw my works for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29988L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29988L\"></sup>forty years.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Therefore I was provoked with that generation,and said, ‘They always go astray in their heart;they have not known my ways.’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29990M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29990M\"></sup>As I swore in my wrath,‘They shall not enter my rest.’”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Take care, brothers, lest there be in any of you an evil, unbelieving heart, leading you to fall away from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29991N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29991N\"></sup>the living God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29992O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29992O\"></sup>exhort one another every day, as long as it is called “today,” that none of you may be hardened by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29992P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29992P\"></sup>the deceitfulness of sin.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For we have come to share in Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29993Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29993Q\"></sup>if indeed we hold our original confidence firm to the end.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>As it is said,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29994R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29994R\"></sup>“Today, if you hear his voice,do not harden your hearts as in the rebellion.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29995S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29995S\"></sup>who were those who heard and yet rebelled? Was it not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29995T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29995T\"></sup>all those who left Egypt led by Moses?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And with whom was he provoked for forty years? Was it not with those who sinned, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29996U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29996U\"></sup>whose bodies fell in the wilderness?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And to whom did he swear that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29997V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29997V\"></sup>they would not enter his rest, but to those who were disobedient?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So we see that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29998W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29998W\"></sup>they were unable to enter because of unbelief."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Therefore, while the promise of entering his rest still stands, let us fear lest any of you should seem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29999A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29999A\"></sup>to have failed to reach it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For good news came to us just as to them, but the message they heard did not benefit them, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30000B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30000B\"></sup>they were not united by faith with those who listened.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For we who have believed enter that rest, as he has said,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30001C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30001C\"></sup>“As I swore in my wrath,‘They shall not enter my rest,’”although his works were finished from the foundation of the world.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For he has somewhere spoken of the seventh day in this way: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30002D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30002D\"></sup>“And God rested on the seventh day from all his works.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And again in this passage he said,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30003E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30003E\"></sup>“They shall not enter my rest.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Since therefore it remains for some to enter it, and those who formerly received the good news <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30004F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30004F\"></sup>failed to enter because of disobedience,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>again he appoints a certain day, “Today,” saying through David so long afterward, in the words already quoted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30005G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30005G\"></sup>“Today, if you hear his voice,do not harden your hearts.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For if Joshua had given them rest, God would not have spoken of another day later on.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So then, there remains a Sabbath rest for the people of God,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>for whoever has entered God's rest has also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30008H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30008H\"></sup>rested from his works as God did from his.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Let us therefore strive to enter that rest, so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30009I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30009I\"></sup>that no one may fall by the same sort of disobedience.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30010J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30010J\"></sup>the word of God is living and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30010K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30010K\"></sup>active, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30010L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30010L\"></sup>sharper than any <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30010M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30010M\"></sup>two-edged sword, piercing to the division of soul and of spirit, of joints and of marrow, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30010N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30010N\"></sup>discerning the thoughts and intentions of the heart.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30011O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30011O\"></sup>no creature is hidden from his sight, but all are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30011P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30011P\"></sup>naked and exposed to the eyes of him to whom we must give account.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Since then we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30012Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30012Q\"></sup>a great high priest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30012R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30012R\"></sup>who has passed through the heavens, Jesus, the Son of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30012S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30012S\"></sup>let us hold fast our confession.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For we do not have a high priest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30013T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30013T\"></sup>who is unable to sympathize with our weaknesses, but one who in every respect has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30013U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30013U\"></sup>tempted as we are, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30013V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30013V\"></sup>yet without sin.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30014W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30014W\"></sup>Let us then with confidence draw near to the throne of grace, that we may receive mercy and find grace to help in time of need."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>For every high priest chosen from among men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30015A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30015A\"></sup>is appointed to act on behalf of men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30015B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30015B\"></sup>in relation to God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30015C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30015C\"></sup>to offer gifts and sacrifices for sins.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30016D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30016D\"></sup>He can deal gently with the ignorant and wayward, since he himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30016E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30016E\"></sup>is beset with weakness.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Because of this he is obligated to offer sacrifice for his own sins <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30017F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30017F\"></sup>just as he does for those of the people.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30018G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30018G\"></sup>no one takes this honor for himself, but only when called by God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30018H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30018H\"></sup>just as Aaron was.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So also Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30019I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30019I\"></sup>did not exalt himself to be made a high priest, but was appointed by him who said to him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30019J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30019J\"></sup>“You are my Son,today I have begotten you”;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>as he says also in another place,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30020K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30020K\"></sup>“You are a priest forever,after the order of Melchizedek.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>In the days of his flesh, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30021L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30021L\"></sup>Jesus offered up prayers and supplications, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30021M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30021M\"></sup>with loud cries and tears, to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30021N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30021N\"></sup>who was able to save him from death, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30021O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30021O\"></sup>he was heard because of his reverence.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Although <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30022P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30022P\"></sup>he was a son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30022Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30022Q\"></sup>he learned obedience through what he suffered.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30023R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30023R\"></sup>being made perfect, he became the source of eternal salvation to all who obey him,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>being designated by God a high priest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30024S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30024S\"></sup>after the order of Melchizedek.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>About this we have much to say, and it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30025T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30025T\"></sup>hard to explain, since you have become dull of hearing.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For though by this time you ought to be teachers, you need someone to teach you again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30026U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30026U\"></sup>the basic principles of the oracles of God. You need <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30026V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30026V\"></sup>milk, not solid food,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>for everyone who lives on milk is unskilled in the word of righteousness, since he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30027W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30027W\"></sup>a child.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But solid food is for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30028X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30028X\"></sup>the mature, for those who have their powers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30028Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30028Y\"></sup>of discernment trained by constant practice to distinguish good from evil."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30029A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30029A\"></sup>let us leave <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30029B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30029B\"></sup>the elementary doctrine of Christ and go on to maturity, not laying again a foundation of repentance <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30029C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30029C\"></sup>from dead works and of faith toward God,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30030D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30030D\"></sup>instruction about washings, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30030E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30030E\"></sup>the laying on of hands, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30030F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30030F\"></sup>the resurrection of the dead, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30030G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30030G\"></sup>eternal judgment.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And this we will do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30031H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30031H\"></sup>if God permits.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For it is impossible, in the case of those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30032I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30032I\"></sup>who have once been enlightened, who have tasted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30032J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30032J\"></sup>the heavenly gift, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30032K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30032K\"></sup>have shared in the Holy Spirit,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30033L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30033L\"></sup>have tasted the goodness of the word of God and the powers of the age to come,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30034M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30034M\"></sup>then have fallen away, to restore them again to repentance, since <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30034N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30034N\"></sup>they are crucifying once again the Son of God to their own harm and holding him up to contempt.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30035O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30035O\"></sup>land that has drunk the rain that often falls on it, and produces a crop useful to those for whose sake it is cultivated, receives a blessing from God.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30036P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30036P\"></sup>if it bears thorns and thistles, it is worthless and near to being cursed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30036Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30036Q\"></sup>and its end is to be burned.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Though we speak in this way, yet in your case, beloved, we feel sure of better things—things that belong to salvation.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30038R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30038R\"></sup>God is not unjust so as to overlook <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30038S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30038S\"></sup>your work and the love that you have shown for his name in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30038T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30038T\"></sup>serving the saints, as you still do.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And we desire each one of you to show the same earnestness to have the full assurance <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30039U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30039U\"></sup>of hope until the end,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>so that you may not be sluggish, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30040V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30040V\"></sup>imitators of those who through faith and patience inherit the promises.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For when God made a promise to Abraham, since he had no one greater by whom to swear, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30041W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30041W\"></sup>he swore by himself,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30042X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30042X\"></sup>“Surely I will bless you and multiply you.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And thus Abraham, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30043Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30043Y\"></sup>having patiently waited, obtained the promise.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For people swear by something greater than themselves, and in all their disputes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30044Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30044Z\"></sup>an oath is final for confirmation.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So when God desired to show more convincingly to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30045AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30045AA\"></sup>the heirs of the promise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30045AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30045AB\"></sup>the unchangeable character of his purpose, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30045AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30045AC\"></sup>he guaranteed it with an oath,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>so that by two unchangeable things, in which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30046AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30046AD\"></sup>it is impossible for God to lie, we who have fled for refuge might have strong encouragement to hold fast to the hope <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30046AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30046AE\"></sup>set before us.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>We have this as a sure and steadfast anchor of the soul, a hope that enters into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30047AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30047AF\"></sup>the inner place behind the curtain,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>where Jesus has gone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30048AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30048AG\"></sup>as a forerunner on our behalf, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30048AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30048AH\"></sup>having become a high priest forever after the order of Melchizedek."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>For this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30049A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30049A\"></sup>Melchizedek, king of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30049B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30049B\"></sup>Salem, priest of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30049C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30049C\"></sup>the Most High God, met Abraham returning from the slaughter of the kings and blessed him,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and to him Abraham apportioned a tenth part of everything. He is first, by translation of his name, king of righteousness, and then he is also king of Salem, that is, king of peace.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He is without father or mother <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30051D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30051D\"></sup>or genealogy, having neither beginning of days nor end of life, but resembling the Son of God he continues a priest forever.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>See how great this man was to whom Abraham <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30052E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30052E\"></sup>the patriarch gave a tenth of the spoils!",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30053F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30053F\"></sup>those descendants of Levi who receive the priestly office have a commandment in the law to take tithes from the people, that is, from their brothers, though these also are descended from Abraham.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But this man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30054G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30054G\"></sup>who does not have his descent from them received tithes from Abraham and blessed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30054H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30054H\"></sup>him who had the promises.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>It is beyond dispute that the inferior is blessed by the superior.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In the one case tithes are received by mortal men, but in the other case, by one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30056I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30056I\"></sup>of whom it is testified that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30056J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30056J\"></sup>he lives.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>One might even say that Levi himself, who receives tithes, paid tithes through Abraham,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>for he was still in the loins of his ancestor when Melchizedek met him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30059K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30059K\"></sup>Now if perfection had been attainable through the Levitical priesthood (for under it the people received the law), what further need would there have been for another priest to arise after the order of Melchizedek, rather than one named after the order of Aaron?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For when there is a change in the priesthood, there is necessarily a change in the law as well.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For the one of whom these things are spoken belonged to another tribe, from which no one has ever served at the altar.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For it is evident that our Lord was descended <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30062L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30062L\"></sup>from Judah, and in connection with that tribe Moses said nothing about priests.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>This becomes even more evident when another priest arises in the likeness of Melchizedek,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>who has become a priest, not on the basis of a legal requirement concerning bodily descent, but by the power of an indestructible life.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For it is witnessed of him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30065M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30065M\"></sup>“You are a priest forever,after the order of Melchizedek.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For on the one hand, a former commandment is set aside <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30066N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30066N\"></sup>because of its weakness and uselessness",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>(for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30067O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30067O\"></sup>the law made nothing perfect); but on the other hand, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30067P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30067P\"></sup>a better hope is introduced, through which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30067Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30067Q\"></sup>we draw near to God.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And it was not without an oath. For those who formerly became priests were made such without an oath,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>but this one was made a priest with an oath by the one who said to him:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30069R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30069R\"></sup>“The Lord has swornand will not change his mind,‘You are a priest forever.’”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>This makes Jesus the guarantor of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30070S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30070S\"></sup>a better covenant.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The former priests were many in number, because they were prevented by death from continuing in office,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>but he holds his priesthood permanently, because he continues <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30072T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30072T\"></sup>forever.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Consequently, he is able to save to the uttermost <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30073U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30073U\"></sup>those who draw near to God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30073V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30073V\"></sup>through him, since he always lives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30073W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30073W\"></sup>to make intercession for them.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For it was indeed fitting that we should have such a high priest, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30074X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30074X\"></sup>holy, innocent, unstained, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30074Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30074Y\"></sup>separated from sinners, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30074Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30074Z\"></sup>exalted above the heavens.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>He has no need, like those high priests, to offer sacrifices daily, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30075AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30075AA\"></sup>first for his own sins and then for those of the people, since he did this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30075AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30075AB\"></sup>once for all when he offered up himself.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>For the law appoints men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30076AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30076AC\"></sup>in their weakness as high priests, but the word of the oath, which came later than the law, appoints a Son who has been made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30076AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30076AD\"></sup>perfect forever."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Now the point in what we are saying is this: we have such a high priest, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30077A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30077A\"></sup>one who is seated at the right hand of the throne of the Majesty in heaven,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>a minister in the holy places, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30078B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30078B\"></sup>the true tent that the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30078C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30078C\"></sup>set up, not man.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30079D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30079D\"></sup>every high priest is appointed to offer gifts and sacrifices; thus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30079E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30079E\"></sup>it is necessary for this priest also to have something to offer.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now if he were on earth, he would not be a priest at all, since there are priests who offer gifts according to the law.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They serve <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30081F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30081F\"></sup>a copy and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30081G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30081G\"></sup>shadow of the heavenly things. For when Moses was about to erect the tent, he was instructed by God, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30081H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30081H\"></sup>“See that you make everything according to the pattern that was shown you on the mountain.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But as it is, Christ has obtained a ministry that is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30082I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30082I\"></sup>as much more excellent than the old as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30082J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30082J\"></sup>the covenant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30082K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30082K\"></sup>he mediates is better, since it is enacted on better promises.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30083L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30083L\"></sup>For if that first covenant had been faultless, there would have been no occasion to look for a second.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For he finds fault with them when he says:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30084M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30084M\"></sup>“Behold, the days are coming, declares the Lord,when I will establish a new covenant with the house of Israeland with the house of Judah,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>not like the covenant that I made with their fatherson the day when I took them by the hand to bring them out of the land of Egypt.For they did not continue in my covenant,and so I showed no concern for them, declares the Lord.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30086N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30086N\"></sup>For this is the covenant that I will make with the house of Israelafter those days, declares the Lord:I will put my laws into their minds,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30086O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30086O\"></sup>write them on their hearts,and I will be their God,and they shall be my people.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And they shall not teach, each one his neighborand each one his brother, saying, ‘Know the Lord,’for they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30087P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30087P\"></sup>all know me,from the least of them to the greatest.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For I will be merciful toward their iniquities,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30088Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30088Q\"></sup>and I will remember their sins no more.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>In speaking of a new covenant, he makes the first one obsolete. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30089R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30089R\"></sup>what is becoming obsolete and growing old is ready to vanish away."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Now even the first covenant had regulations for worship and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30090A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30090A\"></sup>an earthly place of holiness.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30091B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30091B\"></sup>a tent was prepared, the first section, in which were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30091C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30091C\"></sup>the lampstand and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30091D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30091D\"></sup>the table and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30091E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30091E\"></sup>the bread of the Presence. It is called the Holy Place.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Behind <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30092F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30092F\"></sup>the second curtain was a second section called the Most Holy Place,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>having the golden <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30093G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30093G\"></sup>altar of incense and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30093H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30093H\"></sup>the ark of the covenant covered on all sides with gold, in which was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30093I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30093I\"></sup>a golden urn holding the manna, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30093J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30093J\"></sup>Aaron's staff that budded, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30093K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30093K\"></sup>the tablets of the covenant.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Above it were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30094L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30094L\"></sup>the cherubim of glory overshadowing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30094M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30094M\"></sup>the mercy seat. Of these things we cannot now speak in detail.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>These preparations having thus been made, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30095N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30095N\"></sup>the priests go regularly into the first section, performing their ritual duties,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>but into the second only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30096O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30096O\"></sup>the high priest goes, and he but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30096P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30096P\"></sup>once a year, and not without taking blood, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30096Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30096Q\"></sup>which he offers for himself and for the unintentional sins of the people.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>By this the Holy Spirit indicates that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30097R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30097R\"></sup>the way into the holy places is not yet opened as long as the first section is still standing",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>(which is symbolic for the present age). According to this arrangement, gifts and sacrifices are offered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30098S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30098S\"></sup>that cannot perfect the conscience of the worshiper,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>but deal only with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30099T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30099T\"></sup>food and drink and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30099U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30099U\"></sup>various washings, regulations for the body imposed until the time of reformation.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But when Christ appeared as a high priest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30100V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30100V\"></sup>of the good things that have come, then through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30100W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30100W\"></sup>the greater and more perfect tent (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30100X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30100X\"></sup>not made with hands, that is, not of this creation)",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30101Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30101Y\"></sup>entered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30101Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30101Z\"></sup>once for all into the holy places, not by means of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30101AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30101AA\"></sup>the blood of goats and calves but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30101AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30101AB\"></sup>by means of his own blood, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30101AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30101AC\"></sup>thus securing an eternal redemption.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30102AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30102AD\"></sup>the blood of goats and bulls, and the sprinkling of defiled persons with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30102AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30102AE\"></sup>the ashes of a heifer, sanctify for the purification of the flesh,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>how much more will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30103AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30103AF\"></sup>the blood of Christ, who through the eternal Spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30103AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30103AG\"></sup>offered himself without blemish to God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30103AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30103AH\"></sup>purify our conscience <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30103AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30103AI\"></sup>from dead works <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30103AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30103AJ\"></sup>to serve the living God.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30104AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30104AK\"></sup>the mediator of a new covenant, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30104AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30104AL\"></sup>those who are called may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30104AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30104AM\"></sup>receive the promised eternal inheritance, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30104AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30104AN\"></sup>since a death has occurred that redeems them from the transgressions committed under the first covenant.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For where a will is involved, the death of the one who made it must be established.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30106AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30106AO\"></sup>a will takes effect only at death, since it is not in force as long as the one who made it is alive.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore not even the first covenant was inaugurated <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30107AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30107AP\"></sup>without blood.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For when every commandment of the law had been declared by Moses to all the people, he took <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30108AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30108AQ\"></sup>the blood of calves and goats, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30108AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30108AR\"></sup>with water and scarlet wool and hyssop, and sprinkled both the book itself and all the people,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30109AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30109AS\"></sup>“This is the blood of the covenant that God commanded for you.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And in the same way he sprinkled with the blood both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30110AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30110AT\"></sup>the tent and all the vessels used in worship.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Indeed, under the law almost everything is purified with blood, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30111AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30111AU\"></sup>without the shedding of blood there is no forgiveness of sins.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Thus it was necessary for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30112AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30112AV\"></sup>the copies of the heavenly things to be purified with these rites, but the heavenly things themselves with better sacrifices than these.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For Christ has entered, not into holy places <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30113AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30113AW\"></sup>made with hands, which are copies of the true things, but into heaven itself, now to appear in the presence of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30113AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30113AX\"></sup>on our behalf.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Nor was it to offer himself repeatedly, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30114AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30114AY\"></sup>the high priest enters <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30114AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30114AZ\"></sup>the holy places every year with blood not his own,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>for then he would have had to suffer repeatedly since the foundation of the world. But as it is, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30115BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30115BA\"></sup>he has appeared <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30115BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30115BB\"></sup>once for all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30115BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30115BC\"></sup>at the end of the ages to put away sin by the sacrifice of himself.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30116BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30116BD\"></sup>it is appointed for man to die once, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30116BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30116BE\"></sup>after that comes judgment,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>so Christ, having been offered once <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30117BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30117BF\"></sup>to bear the sins of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30117BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30117BG\"></sup>many, will appear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30117BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30117BH\"></sup>a second time, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30117BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30117BI\"></sup>not to deal with sin but to save those who are eagerly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30117BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30117BJ\"></sup>waiting for him."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>For since the law has but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30118A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30118A\"></sup>a shadow <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30118B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30118B\"></sup>of the good things to come instead of the true form of these realities, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30118C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30118C\"></sup>it can never, by the same sacrifices that are continually offered every year, make perfect those who draw near.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Otherwise, would they not have ceased to be offered, since the worshipers, having once been cleansed, would no longer have any consciousness of sins?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30120D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30120D\"></sup>in these sacrifices <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30120E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30120E\"></sup>there is a reminder of sins every year.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30121F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30121F\"></sup>it is impossible for the blood of bulls and goats to take away sins.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Consequently, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30122G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30122G\"></sup>when Christ came into the world, he said,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30122H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30122H\"></sup>“Sacrifices and offerings you have not desired,but a body have you prepared for me;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>in burnt offerings and sin offeringsyou have taken no pleasure.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then I said, ‘Behold, I have come to do your will, O God,as it is written of me in the scroll of the book.’”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When he said above, “You have neither desired nor taken pleasure in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30125I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30125I\"></sup>sacrifices and offerings and burnt offerings and sin offerings” (these are offered according to the law),",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>then he added, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30126J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30126J\"></sup>“Behold, I have come to do your will.” He does away with the first in order to establish the second.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And by that will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30127K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30127K\"></sup>we have been sanctified through the offering of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30127L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30127L\"></sup>the body of Jesus Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30127M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30127M\"></sup>once for all.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And every priest stands <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30128N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30128N\"></sup>daily at his service, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30128O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30128O\"></sup>offering repeatedly the same sacrifices, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30128P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30128P\"></sup>which can never take away sins.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But when Christ had offered for all time a single sacrifice for sins, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30129Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30129Q\"></sup>sat down at the right hand of God,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>waiting from that time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30130R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30130R\"></sup>until his enemies should be made a footstool for his feet.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For by a single offering <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30131S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30131S\"></sup>he has perfected for all time those who are being sanctified.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And the Holy Spirit also bears witness to us; for after saying,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30133T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30133T\"></sup>“This is the covenant that I will make with themafter those days, declares the Lord:I will put my laws on their hearts,and write them on their minds,”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>then he adds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30134U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30134U\"></sup>“I will remember their sins and their lawless deeds no more.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Where there is forgiveness of these, there is no longer any offering for sin.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30136V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30136V\"></sup>Therefore, brothers, since we have confidence to enter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30136W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30136W\"></sup>the holy places by the blood of Jesus,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30137X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30137X\"></sup>the new and living way that he opened for us through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30137Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30137Y\"></sup>the curtain, that is, through his flesh,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>and since we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30138Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30138Z\"></sup>a great priest over the house of God,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>let us draw near with a true heart in full assurance of faith, with our hearts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30139AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30139AA\"></sup>sprinkled clean <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30139AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30139AB\"></sup>from an evil conscience and our bodies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30139AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30139AC\"></sup>washed with pure water.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30140AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30140AD\"></sup>Let us hold fast the confession of our hope without wavering, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30140AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30140AE\"></sup>he who promised is faithful.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30141AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30141AF\"></sup>let us consider how to stir up one another to love and good works,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30142AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30142AG\"></sup>not neglecting to meet together, as is the habit of some, but encouraging one another, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30142AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30142AH\"></sup>all the more as you see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30142AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30142AI\"></sup>the Day drawing near.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30143AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30143AJ\"></sup>if we go on sinning deliberately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30143AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30143AK\"></sup>after receiving the knowledge of the truth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30143AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30143AL\"></sup>there no longer remains a sacrifice for sins,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30144AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30144AM\"></sup>but a fearful expectation of judgment, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30144AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30144AN\"></sup>a fury of fire that will consume the adversaries.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30145AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30145AO\"></sup>Anyone who has set aside the law of Moses dies without mercy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30145AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30145AP\"></sup>on the evidence of two or three witnesses.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>How much worse punishment, do you think, will be deserved by the one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30146AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30146AQ\"></sup>who has trampled underfoot the Son of God, and has profaned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30146AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30146AR\"></sup>the blood of the covenant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30146AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30146AS\"></sup>by which he was sanctified, and has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30146AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30146AT\"></sup>outraged the Spirit of grace?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>For we know him who said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30147AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30147AU\"></sup>“Vengeance is mine; I will repay.” And again, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30147AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30147AV\"></sup>“The Lord will judge his people.”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30148AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30148AW\"></sup>It is a fearful thing to fall into the hands of the living God.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>But recall the former days when, after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30149AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30149AX\"></sup>you were enlightened, you endured <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30149AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30149AY\"></sup>a hard struggle with sufferings,",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>sometimes being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30150AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30150AZ\"></sup>publicly exposed to reproach and affliction, and sometimes being partners with those so treated.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30151BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30151BA\"></sup>you had compassion on those in prison, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30151BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30151BB\"></sup>you joyfully accepted the plundering of your property, since you knew that you yourselves had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30151BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30151BC\"></sup>a better possession and an abiding one.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Therefore do not throw away your confidence, which has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30152BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30152BD\"></sup>a great reward.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30153BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30153BE\"></sup>you have need of endurance, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30153BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30153BF\"></sup>when you have done the will of God you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30153BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30153BG\"></sup>receive what is promised.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>For,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30154BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30154BH\"></sup>“Yet a little while,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30154BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30154BI\"></sup>the coming one will come and will not delay;",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30155BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30155BJ\"></sup>but my righteous one shall live by faith,and if he shrinks back,my soul has no pleasure in him.”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>But we are not of those who shrink back and are destroyed, but of those who have faith and preserve their souls."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Now faith is the assurance of things hoped for, the conviction of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30157A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30157A\"></sup>things not seen.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For by it the people of old received their commendation.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>By faith we understand that the universe was created by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30159B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30159B\"></sup>the word of God, so that what is seen was not made out of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30159C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30159C\"></sup>things that are visible.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30160D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30160D\"></sup>Abel offered to God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30160E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30160E\"></sup>a more acceptable sacrifice than Cain, through which he was commended as righteous, God commending him by accepting his gifts. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30160F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30160F\"></sup>through his faith, though he died, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30160G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30160G\"></sup>still speaks.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30161H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30161H\"></sup>Enoch was taken up so that he should not see death, and he was not found, because God had taken him. Now before he was taken he was commended as having pleased God.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And without faith it is impossible to please him, for whoever would draw near to God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30162I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30162I\"></sup>must believe that he exists and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30162J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30162J\"></sup>that he rewards those who seek him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30163K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30163K\"></sup>Noah, being warned by God concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30163L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30163L\"></sup>events as yet unseen, in reverent fear constructed an ark for the saving of his household. By this he condemned the world and became an heir of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30163M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30163M\"></sup>the righteousness that comes by faith.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30164N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30164N\"></sup>Abraham obeyed when he was called to go out to a place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30164O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30164O\"></sup>that he was to receive as an inheritance. And he went out, not knowing where he was going.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>By faith he went to live in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30165P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30165P\"></sup>the land of promise, as in a foreign land, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30165Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30165Q\"></sup>living in tents <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30165R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30165R\"></sup>with Isaac and Jacob, heirs with him of the same promise.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For he was looking forward to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30166S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30166S\"></sup>the city that has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30166T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30166T\"></sup>foundations, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30166U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30166U\"></sup>whose designer and builder is God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30167V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30167V\"></sup>Sarah herself received power to conceive, even when she was past the age, since she considered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30167W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30167W\"></sup>him faithful who had promised.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore from one man, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30168X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30168X\"></sup>him as good as dead, were born descendants <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30168Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30168Y\"></sup>as many as the stars of heaven and as many as the innumerable grains of sand by the seashore.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>These all died in faith, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30169Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30169Z\"></sup>not having received the things promised, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30169AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30169AA\"></sup>having seen them and greeted them from afar, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30169AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30169AB\"></sup>having acknowledged that they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30169AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30169AC\"></sup>strangers and exiles on the earth.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For people who speak thus make it clear that they are seeking a homeland.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If they had been thinking of that land from which they had gone out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30171AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30171AD\"></sup>they would have had opportunity to return.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But as it is, they desire a better country, that is, a heavenly one. Therefore God is not ashamed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30172AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30172AE\"></sup>to be called their God, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30172AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30172AF\"></sup>he has prepared for them a city.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30173AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30173AG\"></sup>Abraham, when he was tested, offered up Isaac, and he who had received the promises was in the act of offering up his only son,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>of whom it was said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30174AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30174AH\"></sup>“Through Isaac shall your offspring be named.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30175AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30175AI\"></sup>He considered that God was able even to raise him from the dead, from which, figuratively speaking, he did receive him back.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30176AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30176AJ\"></sup>Isaac invoked future blessings on Jacob and Esau.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30177AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30177AK\"></sup>Jacob, when dying, blessed each of the sons of Joseph, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30177AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30177AL\"></sup>bowing in worship over the head of his staff.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30178AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30178AM\"></sup>Joseph, at the end of his life, made mention of the exodus of the Israelites and gave directions concerning his bones.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30179AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30179AN\"></sup>Moses, when he was born, was hidden for three months by his parents, because they saw that the child was beautiful, and they were not afraid of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30179AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30179AO\"></sup>the king's edict.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>By faith Moses, when he was grown up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30180AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30180AP\"></sup>refused to be called the son of Pharaoh's daughter,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30181AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30181AQ\"></sup>choosing rather to be mistreated with the people of God than to enjoy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30181AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30181AR\"></sup>the fleeting pleasures of sin.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30182AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30182AS\"></sup>He considered the reproach of Christ greater wealth than the treasures of Egypt, for he was looking to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30182AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30182AT\"></sup>the reward.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>By faith he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30183AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30183AU\"></sup>left Egypt, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30183AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30183AV\"></sup>not being afraid of the anger of the king, for he endured <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30183AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30183AW\"></sup>as seeing him who is invisible.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30184AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30184AX\"></sup>he kept the Passover and sprinkled the blood, so that the Destroyer of the firstborn might not touch them.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30185AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30185AY\"></sup>the people crossed the Red Sea as on dry land, but the Egyptians, when they attempted to do the same, were drowned.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30186AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30186AZ\"></sup>the walls of Jericho fell down after they had been encircled for seven days.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30187BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30187BA\"></sup>Rahab the prostitute did not perish with those who were disobedient, because she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30187BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30187BB\"></sup>had given a friendly welcome to the spies.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And what more shall I say? For time would fail me to tell of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30188BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30188BC\"></sup>Gideon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30188BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30188BD\"></sup>Barak, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30188BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30188BE\"></sup>Samson, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30188BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30188BF\"></sup>Jephthah, of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30188BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30188BG\"></sup>David and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30188BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30188BH\"></sup>Samuel and the prophets—",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>who through faith conquered kingdoms, enforced justice, obtained promises, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30189BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30189BI\"></sup>stopped the mouths of lions,",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30190BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30190BJ\"></sup>quenched the power of fire, escaped the edge of the sword, were made strong out of weakness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30190BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30190BK\"></sup>became mighty in war, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30190BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30190BL\"></sup>put foreign armies to flight.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30191BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30191BM\"></sup>Women received back their dead by resurrection. Some were tortured, refusing to accept release, so that they might rise again to a better life.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Others suffered mocking and flogging, and even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30192BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30192BN\"></sup>chains and imprisonment.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30193BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30193BO\"></sup>They were stoned, they were sawn in two, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30193BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30193BP\"></sup>they were killed with the sword. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30193BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30193BQ\"></sup>They went about in skins of sheep and goats, destitute, afflicted, mistreated—",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>of whom the world was not worthy—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30194BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30194BR\"></sup>wandering about in deserts and mountains, and in dens and caves of the earth.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And all these, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30195BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30195BS\"></sup>though commended through their faith, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30195BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30195BT\"></sup>did not receive what was promised,",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>since God had provided something better for us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30196BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30196BU\"></sup>that apart from us they should not be made perfect."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Therefore, since we are surrounded by so great a cloud of witnesses, let us also lay aside every weight, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30197A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30197A\"></sup>sin which clings so closely, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30197B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30197B\"></sup>let us run <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30197C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30197C\"></sup>with endurance the race that is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30197D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30197D\"></sup>set before us,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>looking to Jesus, the founder and perfecter of our faith, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30198E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30198E\"></sup>who for the joy that was set before him endured the cross, despising <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30198F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30198F\"></sup>the shame, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30198G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30198G\"></sup>is seated at the right hand of the throne of God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30199H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30199H\"></sup>Consider him who endured from sinners such hostility against himself, so that you may not grow weary or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30199I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30199I\"></sup>fainthearted.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>In your struggle against sin you have not yet resisted to the point of shedding your blood.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And have you forgotten the exhortation that addresses you as sons?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30201J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30201J\"></sup>“My son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30201K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30201K\"></sup>do not regard lightly the discipline of the Lord,nor be weary when reproved by him.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30202L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30202L\"></sup>the Lord disciplines the one he loves,and chastises every son whom he receives.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>It is for discipline that you have to endure. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30203M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30203M\"></sup>God is treating you as sons. For what son is there whom his father does not discipline?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>If you are left without discipline, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30204N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30204N\"></sup>in which all have participated, then you are illegitimate children and not sons.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Besides this, we have had earthly fathers who disciplined us and we respected them. Shall we not much more be subject to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30205O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30205O\"></sup>the Father of spirits <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30205P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30205P\"></sup>and live?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For they disciplined us for a short time as it seemed best to them, but he disciplines us for our good, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30206Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30206Q\"></sup>that we may share his holiness.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30207R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30207R\"></sup>For the moment all discipline seems painful rather than pleasant, but later it yields <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30207S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30207S\"></sup>the peaceful fruit of righteousness to those who have been trained by it.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30208T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30208T\"></sup>lift your drooping hands and strengthen your weak knees,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30209U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30209U\"></sup>make straight paths for your feet, so that what is lame may not be put out of joint <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30209V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30209V\"></sup>but rather be healed.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30210W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30210W\"></sup>Strive for peace with everyone, and for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30210X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30210X\"></sup>holiness <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30210Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30210Y\"></sup>without which no one will see the Lord.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>See to it that no one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30211Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30211Z\"></sup>fails to obtain the grace of God; that no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30211AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30211AA\"></sup>“root of bitterness” springs up and causes trouble, and by it many become defiled;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>that no one is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30212AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30212AB\"></sup>sexually immoral or unholy like Esau, who sold his birthright for a single meal.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For you know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30213AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30213AC\"></sup>afterward, when he desired to inherit the blessing, he was rejected, for he found no chance to repent, though he sought it with tears.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For you have not come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30214AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30214AD\"></sup>what may be touched, a blazing fire and darkness and gloom and a tempest",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30215AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30215AE\"></sup>the sound of a trumpet and a voice whose words <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30215AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30215AF\"></sup>made the hearers beg that no further messages be spoken to them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For they could not endure the order that was given, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30216AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30216AG\"></sup>“If even a beast touches the mountain, it shall be stoned.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Indeed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30217AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30217AH\"></sup>so terrifying was the sight that Moses said, “I tremble with fear.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But you have come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30218AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30218AI\"></sup>Mount Zion and to the city of the living God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30218AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30218AJ\"></sup>the heavenly Jerusalem, and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30218AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30218AK\"></sup>innumerable angels in festal gathering,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30219AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30219AL\"></sup>the assembly of the firstborn who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30219AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30219AM\"></sup>enrolled in heaven, and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30219AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30219AN\"></sup>God, the judge of all, and to the spirits of the righteous made perfect,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and to Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30220AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30220AO\"></sup>the mediator of a new covenant, and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30220AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30220AP\"></sup>the sprinkled blood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30220AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30220AQ\"></sup>that speaks a better word than the blood of Abel.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>See that you do not refuse him who is speaking. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30221AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30221AR\"></sup>if they did not escape when they refused him who warned them on earth, much less will we escape if we reject him who warns from heaven.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>At that time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30222AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30222AS\"></sup>his voice shook the earth, but now he has promised, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30222AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30222AT\"></sup>“Yet once more I will shake not only the earth but also the heavens.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>This phrase, “Yet once more,” indicates <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30223AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30223AU\"></sup>the removal of things that are shaken—that is, things that have been made—in order that the things that cannot be shaken may remain.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Therefore let us be grateful for receiving <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30224AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30224AV\"></sup>a kingdom that cannot be shaken, and thus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30224AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30224AW\"></sup>let us offer to God acceptable worship, with reverence and awe,",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>for our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30225AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30225AX\"></sup>God is a consuming fire."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30226A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30226A\"></sup>brotherly love continue.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30227B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30227B\"></sup>Do not neglect to show hospitality to strangers, for thereby <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30227C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30227C\"></sup>some have entertained angels unawares.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30228D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30228D\"></sup>Remember those who are in prison, as though in prison with them, and those who are mistreated, since you also are in the body.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30229E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30229E\"></sup>Let marriage be held in honor among all, and let the marriage bed be undefiled, for God will judge <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30229F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30229F\"></sup>the sexually immoral and adulterous.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Keep your life <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30230G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30230G\"></sup>free from love of money, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30230H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30230H\"></sup>be content with what you have, for he has said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30230I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30230I\"></sup>“I will never leave you nor forsake you.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So we can confidently say,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30231J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30231J\"></sup>“The Lord is my helper;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30231K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30231K\"></sup>I will not fear;what can man do to me?”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Remember <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30232L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30232L\"></sup>your leaders, those who spoke to you the word of God. Consider the outcome of their way of life, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30232M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30232M\"></sup>imitate their faith.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Jesus Christ is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30233N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30233N\"></sup>the same yesterday and today and forever.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Do not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30234O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30234O\"></sup>led away by diverse and strange teachings, for it is good for the heart to be strengthened by grace, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30234P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30234P\"></sup>not by foods, which have not benefited those devoted to them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>We have an altar <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30235Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30235Q\"></sup>from which those who serve the tent have no right to eat.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30236R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30236R\"></sup>the bodies of those animals whose blood is brought into the holy places by the high priest as a sacrifice for sin are burned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30236S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30236S\"></sup>outside the camp.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So Jesus also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30237T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30237T\"></sup>suffered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30237U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30237U\"></sup>outside the gate in order to sanctify the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30237V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30237V\"></sup>through his own blood.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore let us go to him outside the camp and bear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30238W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30238W\"></sup>the reproach he endured.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30239X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30239X\"></sup>here we have no lasting city, but we seek the city that is to come.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30240Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30240Y\"></sup>Through him then let us continually offer up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30240Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30240Z\"></sup>a sacrifice of praise to God, that is, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30240AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30240AA\"></sup>the fruit of lips that acknowledge his name.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Do not neglect to do good and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30241AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30241AB\"></sup>to share what you have, for such <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30241AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30241AC\"></sup>sacrifices are pleasing to God.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Obey <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30242AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30242AD\"></sup>your leaders and submit to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30242AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30242AE\"></sup>for they are keeping watch over your souls, as those who will have to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30242AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30242AF\"></sup>give an account. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30242AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30242AG\"></sup>Let them do this with joy and not with groaning, for that would be of no advantage to you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30243AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30243AH\"></sup>Pray for us, for we are sure that we have a clear conscience, desiring to act honorably in all things.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I urge you the more earnestly to do this in order <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30244AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30244AI\"></sup>that I may be restored to you the sooner.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30245AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30245AJ\"></sup>may the God of peace <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30245AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30245AK\"></sup>who brought again from the dead our Lord Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30245AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30245AL\"></sup>the great shepherd of the sheep, by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30245AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30245AM\"></sup>the blood of the eternal covenant,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30246AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30246AN\"></sup>equip you with everything good that you may do his will, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30246AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30246AO\"></sup>working in us that which is pleasing in his sight, through Jesus Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30246AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30246AP\"></sup>to whom be glory forever and ever. Amen.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I appeal to you, brothers, bear with my word of exhortation, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30247AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30247AQ\"></sup>I have written to you briefly.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>You should know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30248AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30248AR\"></sup>our brother Timothy has been released, with whom I shall see you if he comes soon.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Greet all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30249AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30249AS\"></sup>your leaders and all the saints. Those who come from Italy send you greetings.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30250AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30250AT\"></sup>Grace be with all of you."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;